{"title":"春潮曲——京广线一瞥","authors":["韦丘"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——京广线一瞥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韦丘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淅沥沥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华北平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串春消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融了薄冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水多清！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒了麦苗儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂绿缨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墒情好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"媳妇姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着粪车跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辕上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂满红袍花袄……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿油油。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉色桃花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹅黄垂柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光俏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹皱了长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八百里洞庭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十万顷鄱阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船齐发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆高扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱鲤银鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上钩落网……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦线绣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南春酿秋收酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山为江南青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水为江南秀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岭南水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岭南山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松风如酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坪石到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桐花似雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又过韶关！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"习习春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹裂了水田明镜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霏霏细雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠秧苗细浪轻翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岭南儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艳阳天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战天旱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒粒汗珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散射虹彩千万……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方北方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素裹红装；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春潮急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪打浪……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三、三、北京—广州"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}